## Interface: 120005, 120007
## Title: How Rare? — Achievement Rarity
## Notes: Achievement rarity from the Wizzleworks — the share of accounts that have each achievement, on every tooltip, chat line and achievement-panel row, plus an earned toast. Data by the Wizzleworks.
## Author: the Wizzleworks
## Version: 1.0.2
## SavedVariables: HowRareDB
## OptionalDeps: AchievementRarity
## IconTexture: Interface\Icons\INV_Misc_Gem_Diamond_07
