## Category-enUS: Collections

# Embedded AchievementRarity library (data by the Wizzleworks) — loads before
# Core, which delegates every rarity lookup to it. LibStub first, then the
# generated snapshot, then the library's read API. OptionalDeps above
# guarantees the standalone AchievementRarity addon (if installed) loads
# first, so its fresher data supersedes this embedded copy via LibStub
# minor versioning.
